These results contribute towards\ndeveloping physically-based momentum flux parameterizations for the\nwave-affected boundary layer in ocean circulation models.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 7 May 2018 15:32:50 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-12-05"}
